name: PS-BURROUGHS 1.1
description:
Pixel sorted portrait of William S Burroughs. Source material is the photograph “William Burroughs” by Robert Mapplethorpe, 1980

This generative artwork was created with pixel sorting with Processing p5js. Images are presented as created by code, with no post processing.
